author: RTÉ News
title: China factory gate prices fall further on Covid fears
description: China's factory gate prices fell the most in five months in March, with deflation deepening and set to worsen in coming months as the economic damage wrought by the coronavirus outbreak at home and worldwide shuts down many countries.
